    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Take your favorite beverage anywhere with the ASR Outdoor Stainless Steel Flask and Funnel Bundle. Crafted from durable 201 stainless steel, choose from a 6oz or 8oz flask that are built to resist rust and corrosion, while maintaining a polished, modern look. The included 304 stainless steel funnel ensures mess-free filling, so you never waste a drop.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 2pc Stainless Steel Flask and Funnel Set Hiking Camping (2 Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Take your favorite beverage anywhere with the ASR Outdoor Stainless Steel Flask and Funnel Bundle. Crafted from durable 201 stainless steel, choose from a 6oz or 8oz flask that are built to resist rust and corrosion, while maintaining a polished, modern look. The included 304 stainless steel funnel ensures mess-free filling, so you never waste a drop.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>CONVENIENT STAINLESS STEEL FUNNEL - Funnel features a 1.5&quot; mouth and 3/8&quot; spout for a clean, spill-free pour - perfectly sized for filling flasks or small bottles with your favorite spirits.</li>\n    <li>DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Flask made from 201 stainless steel for lasting durability, resistance to rust and corrosion, and a sleek brushed finish that looks great and stands up to everyday use.</li>\n    <li>PREMIUM FUNNEL INCLUDED - 304 stainless steel funnel makes filling the flask easy and spill-free, ensuring every drop counts. Perfect size for the flask opening.</li>\n    <li>PORTABLE AND COMPACT SIZE – Available in 6oz or 8oz capacity, the slim, curved design fits comfortably in a pocket, jacket, or small bag - ideal for travel, hiking, camping, festivals, and more.</li>\n    <li>SECURE SCREW ON CAP – Attached leak-proof lid prevents spills and loss of the cap, giving you peace of mind when carrying your favorite spirits.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72363/OpZ4RBQbeDML90C1feSOME7LJF22wk-metaQVNST19zc19mdW5uZWxfYW5kX2ZsYXNrc19tYWluLnBuZw==-.png\" alt=\"Take your favorite beverage anywhere with the ASR Outdoor Stainless Steel Flask and Funnel Bundle\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p>The stainless steel flasks features a slim, curved profile that fits comfortably into pockets, bags, or packs, making it the perfect companion for camping, hiking, concerts, tailgates and more. A secure, screw-on cap is attached to the flask to prevent leaks and keep your lid from getting lost.</p>\n  <p>Whether you’re gifting a groomsmen party, preparing for outdoor adventures, or simply looking for a reliable and stylish way to carry your favorite liquor, this stainless steel flask and funnel set is a practical choice. Durable, portable, timeless, and ready to go wherever you do.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
